What you need to know:

Nyongo said the late Kake was one of the greatest hockey players in East and Central Africa during his time."Besides captaining the lethal Kisumu Simba to become the top hockey team in Kenya, Kake also dribbled his way to the National team and played one of his best games ever, during the Olympics," explained Nyongo, adding that his humility and the magic hockey stick put Kisumu on the international map.Â 